The quake ' s shallow depth , less than 8 miles , likely magnified the impactSome 18 , 000 soldiers and armed police were sent to the disaster zone in sourthwestern China , and 10 , 000 had already reached seriously affected areas , the Chengdu Military Area Command said Sunday , according to state news agency Xinhua . The Chengdu Military Area Command also said it would send 23 helicopters .